-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana,geneva;&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;&quot; src=&quot;http:\\/\\/khoemoingay.com\\/images\\/stories\\/20120513\\/20120510afamilySKchienthuatduytrisuckhoe-2_68fbe.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;20120510afamilySKchienthuatduytrisuckhoe-2_68fbe&quot; width=&quot;500&quot; height=&quot;694&quot; \\/&gt;&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;\\r\\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;Iacute;t gi\\u1eadn d\\u1eef&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/strong&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;\\r\\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;M&amp;ugrave;a  h&amp;egrave; kh&amp;ocirc; v&amp;agrave; n&amp;oacute;ng, v\\u1edbi s\\u1ef1 t\\u0103ng t\\u1ed1c c\\u1ee7a l\\u01b0u th&amp;ocirc;ng m&amp;aacute;u khi\\u1ebfn t&amp;acirc;m tr\\u1ea1ng con  ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d\\u1ec5 bi\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1ed9ng. B\\u1ea1n d\\u1ec5 c\\u1ea3m th\\u1ea5y m\\u1ec7t m\\u1ecfi, k&amp;iacute;ch \\u0111\\u1ed9ng, t\\u1ee9c gi\\u1eadn, \\u0111&amp;ocirc;i  khi kh&amp;oacute; ch\\u1ecbu, m\\u1ea5t ng\\u1ee7 ban \\u0111&amp;ecirc;m... Trong t&amp;acirc;m l&amp;yacute; h\\u1ecdc g\\u1ecdi l&amp;agrave; Nhi\\u1ec7t t&amp;igrave;nh c\\u1ea3m,  c&amp;ograve;n g\\u1ecdi l&amp;agrave; &amp;ldquo;R\\u1ed1i lo\\u1ea1n t&amp;igrave;nh c\\u1ea3m m&amp;ugrave;a h&amp;egrave;&amp;rdquo;. S\\u1ef1 b\\u1ea5t \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh v\\u1ec1 c\\u1ea3m x&amp;uacute;c n&amp;agrave;y  r\\u1ea5t nguy hi\\u1ec3m cho ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi cao tu\\u1ed5i, d\\u1ec5 d\\u1eabn \\u0111\\u1ebfn b\\u1ec7nh tim m\\u1ea1ch v&amp;agrave; m\\u1ea1ch m&amp;aacute;u  n&amp;atilde;o. V&amp;igrave; th\\u1ebf, duy tr&amp;igrave; t&amp;igrave;nh c\\u1ea3m \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh v&amp;agrave; r&amp;egrave;n luy\\u1ec7n kh\\u1ea3 n\\u0103ng ch\\u1ecbu \\u0111\\u1ef1ng l&amp;agrave;  \\u0111i\\u1ec1u quan tr\\u1ecdng.&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;\\r\\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;\\u0110\\u1ec3  duy tr&amp;igrave; s\\u1ef1 \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh c\\u1ee7a T&amp;acirc;m, b\\u1ea1n c&amp;oacute; th\\u1ec3 th\\u1eed nghi\\u1ec7m ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph&amp;aacute;p kh&amp;iacute; c&amp;ocirc;ng  d\\u01b0\\u1edbi \\u0111&amp;acirc;y. T&amp;igrave;m m\\u1ed9t c&amp;ocirc;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;acirc;y xanh hay m\\u1ed9t kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian tho&amp;aacute;ng m&amp;aacute;t, b\\u1ea1n  \\u0111\\u1ee9ng tr&amp;ecirc;n m\\u1eb7t \\u0111\\u1ea5t, nh\\u1eafm m\\u1eaft l\\u1ea1i, c&amp;aacute;nh tay r\\u0169 xu\\u1ed1ng t\\u1ef1 nhi&amp;ecirc;n, sau \\u0111&amp;oacute; l\\u1ea5y  m\\u1ed9t h\\u01a1i th\\u1eadt s&amp;acirc;u, t\\u1eeb t\\u1eeb h&amp;iacute;t v&amp;agrave;o b\\u1eb1ng m\\u0169i, b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u t\\u1eeb t\\u1eeb v\\u1edbi v&amp;ograve;ng tay  r\\u1ed9ng m\\u1edf. B\\u1ea1n h&amp;atilde;y t\\u01b0\\u1edfng t\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; \\u0111\\u1ea7y l\\u1ed3ng ng\\u1ef1c, khi \\u0111&amp;oacute; t\\u1eeb t\\u1eeb th\\u1edf  ra th&amp;ocirc;ng qua m\\u0169i v&amp;agrave; b&amp;agrave;n tay t\\u1eeb t\\u1eeb h\\u1ea1 xu\\u1ed1ng.&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;\\r\\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;B&amp;agrave;i  t\\u1eadp th\\u1edf cho ph&amp;eacute;p c\\u01a1 th\\u1ec3 b\\u1ea1n t\\u0103ng th&amp;ecirc;m s\\u1ee9c s\\u1ed1ng v&amp;agrave; ni\\u1ec1m vui, \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t  gi&amp;uacute;p lo\\u1ea1i b\\u1ecf t&amp;igrave;nh tr\\u1ea1ng n&amp;oacute;ng b\\u1ea5t \\u1ed5n. Ngo&amp;agrave;i ra, \\u0103n th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n t\\u01b0\\u01a1i ngon,  th\\u1ee9c \\u0103n nh\\u1eb9 v&amp;agrave; d\\u1ec5 ti&amp;ecirc;u h&amp;oacute;a, \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t l&amp;agrave; d\\u01b0a h\\u1ea5u, d\\u01b0a chu\\u1ed9t, \\u0111&amp;agrave;o v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c  lo\\u1ea1i tr&amp;aacute;i c&amp;acirc;y, rau qu\\u1ea3 theo m&amp;ugrave;a kh&amp;aacute;c. \\u0110\\u1ed1i v\\u1edbi ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi cao tu\\u1ed5i, m&amp;ugrave;a h&amp;egrave; n&amp;ecirc;n  c\\u1ed1 g\\u1eafng r&amp;egrave;n luy\\u1ec7n th&amp;oacute;i quen ng\\u1ee7 tr\\u01b0a. Thi\\u1ebfu ng\\u1ee7 c\\u0169ng l&amp;agrave; m\\u1ed9t l&amp;yacute; do quan  tr\\u1ecdng khi\\u1ebfn cho ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi ta d\\u1ec5 c&amp;aacute;u k\\u1ec9nh.&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;\\r\\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;\\u0102n th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m \\u0111\\u1eafng&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/strong&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;\\r\\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana,geneva; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;M&amp;ugrave;a  h&amp;egrave; n&amp;oacute;ng n\\u1ef1c khi\\u1ebfn cho kh\\u1ea9u v\\u1ecb b\\u1ecb thay \\u0111\\u1ed5i kh&amp;aacute; nhi\\u1ec1u, \\u0111&amp;ocirc;i khi th\\u1ea5y v&amp;ocirc;  v\\u1ecb, ch&amp;aacute;n \\u0103n. V&amp;igrave; th\\u1ebf sau \\u0111&amp;oacute; ch&amp;uacute;ng ta c&amp;oacute; xu h\\u01b0\\u1edbng &amp;eacute;p bu\\u1ed9c b\\u1ea3n th&amp;acirc;n ph\\u1ea3i \\u0103n  c&amp;aacute;c th\\u1ecbt, c&amp;aacute; \\u0111\\u1ec3 b\\u1ed5 sung, v&amp;ocirc; t&amp;igrave;nh l&amp;agrave;m tr\\u1ea7m tr\\u1ecdng th&amp;ecirc;m c&amp;aacute;c tri\\u1ec7u ch\\u1ee9ng  ti&amp;ecirc;u c\\u1ef1c. Tr&amp;aacute;i l\\u1ea1i, \\u0103n c&amp;aacute;c th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m \\u0111\\u1eafng l\\u1ea1i \\u0111&amp;oacute;ng vai tr&amp;ograve; nh\\u01b0 c&amp;aacute;c m&amp;oacute;n  khai v\\u1ecb. C&amp;aacute;c nghi&amp;ecirc;n c\\u1ee9u \\u0111&amp;atilde; ch\\u1ec9 ra r\\u1eb1ng c&amp;aacute;c lo\\u1ea1i th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m cay \\u0111\\u1eafng c&amp;oacute;  ch\\u1ee9a c&amp;aacute;c ch\\u1ea5t nh\\u01b0 alkaloid, axit amin, vitamin, kho&amp;aacute;ng ch\\u1ea5t v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c ch\\u1ea5t  kh&amp;aacute;c c\\u1ea7n thi\\u1ebft cho c\\u01a1